Task::Lingua::PetaMem

Meta-package to install all PetaMem Lingua number conversion modules (all languages, both directions).
Part of the PetaMem Lingua number conversion suite.

INSTALLATION

    shell> cpanm Task::Lingua::PetaMem

    This installs all available languages in both directions.

    For just one direction:

    shell> cpanm Task::Lingua::Word2Num
    shell> cpanm Task::Lingua::Num2Word

